pulls.title: Adding cross references to sections
pulls.author: ajeanmahoney
pulls.body: [Details on xref construction](https://github.com/cabo/kramdown-rfc/wiki/Syntax2#section-references) can be found on the kramdown-rfc wiki.

comments.author: ajeanmahoney
comments.body: Merged this PR so I can check the xrefs in the HTML output.

pulls.title: Fix to "org" property xref
pulls.author: ajeanmahoney
pulls.body: Original had a typo and pointed to section 6.6.2 of RFC 6350. Correct section is [6.6.4.](https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc6350#section-6.6.4)

pulls.title: Move Acknowledgements section to the end
pulls.author: ajeanmahoney

pulls.title: Abbreviate Rich Call Data
pulls.author: ajeanmahoney
pulls.body: After use in the intro. Helps with phrases like "RCD-related Call-Info". Based on advice here: https://www.rfc-editor.org/styleguide/part2/#exp_abbrev

comments.author: chriswendt
comments.body: Looks good, thanks for making that more consistent
